{"word":"προαφίσταμαι","slug":"προαφίσταμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προαφίσταμαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> and aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>:— <i>to fall off</i> or <i>revolt before</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to leave off</i> or <i>desist before</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}